com.stormpath.sdk.hazelcast

Class HazelcastCache<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.stormpath.sdk.hazelcast.HazelcastCache<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - cache key type
    V - cache value type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cache<K,V>

    public class HazelcastCache<K,V>
extends Object
implements Cache<K,V>
    A simple Cache implementation that merely wraps a ConcurrentMap obtained from a HazelcastInstance. The backing Hazelcast-based map is used for all caching operations.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructor and Description
      HazelcastCache(ConcurrentMap<K,V> hazelcastMap)
      Creates a new instance, delegating all caching operations to the specified hazelcastMap.
